(470, 1, '2018-09-25 11:55:49', '2018-09-25 11:55:49', '<p><strong>Segment:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Security, Multimedia, Networking </p>\r\n<p><strong>Short description:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Secure audio processing &amp; management system. </p>\r\n<p><strong>Details:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Audio stream processing (RTSP, RTP, ICY, etc…)</li>\r\n	<li>Audio streams management (convert 3rd party streams to PCM; layer management)</li>\r\n	<li>Unit testing, test cases development</li>\r\n	<li>Inter-process communication (IPC) development</li>\r\n	<li>3rd party protocol processing (Pandora protocol)</li>\r\n	<li>Media utilities development (parsing playlists, metadata, additional info)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Technologies: </strong>C/C++11, Boost, CMake, SVN/Git, CUnit, CppUnit, Qt unit test, Google C++ Testing Framework, SQLite, OpenSSL, Networking, Embedded systems, Linux, Postresql, audio management</p>', 'Audio processing system', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'audio-processing-system', '', '', '2018-10-15 10:58:29', '2018-10-15 10:58:29', '', 0, 'http://demo.pinofran.com/demo/SoftWareSolutionsWP/?p=470', 0, 'post', '', 0),
