(494, 1, '2018-09-25 12:12:15', '2018-09-25 12:12:15', '<p>Project works since 2016.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Customer: </strong>bank</p>\r\n<p><strong>Goal:</strong><br />\r\nThe system allows custom authentication and authorization based upon an LDAP directory. In an organization, users and groups are stored in an LDAP directory. All the intranet applications are supposed to use this directory for authentication and authorization, to implement SSO. Development of common system for these applications to use for such authentication and authorization. A user if logged-in into one application, he should be able to use the other application w/o re-login.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Short description:</strong></p>\r\n<p>The system is composed of the following components: </p>\r\n<p>1. Web application</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Contains a log in page where users accessing intranet applications are redirected for authentication</li>\r\n	<li>Authenticates users against the LDAP directory, for the log in page</li>\r\n	<li>Keeps track of currently authenticated users, for later validations</li>\r\n	<li>Provides authorization data like user groups</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>2. HTTP module</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Provides custom authentication and authorization for the .NET applications</li>\r\n	<li>Authenticates every request to an application</li>\r\n	<li>Reporting</li>\r\n	<li>Administration</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Technologies and libraries:</strong> Webforms, Web API, WCF, WPF, SOAP, Web Services, JSON, AJAX, JS,HTML</p>\r\n<p><strong>Frameworks:</strong> ASP.Net, DevExpress XPO</p>\r\n<p><strong>DB:</strong> MS SQL</p>', 'CREATE THE ARCHITECTURE AND DESIGN OF AN LDAP BASED SINGLE SIGN ON SYSTEM (SSO). IMPLEMENT THE SYSTEM’S SERVICES AND APPLICATIONS', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'endoscopic-irrigation-pump', '', '', '2018-10-15 10:59:28', '2018-10-15 10:59:28', '', 0, 'http://demo.pinofran.com/demo/SoftWareSolutionsWP/?p=494', 0, 'post', '', 0),
