(555, 1, '2018-09-27 15:42:12', '2018-09-27 15:42:12', '<p>Project works since 2015.</p>\n<p><strong>Customer: </strong>government institution</p>\n<p><strong>Goals:</strong><br />\nDevelopment of management system document for the hierarchical organization. Organization must be able to work without paper document. Company management have to get full control on the all stages work with document and task. System have to work with large number of users (more than 15000 users) and to save all documents of customs. System have to provide configuration workflow of document, reports without developers. System must to work using web-technologies and to provide 7-24 service. <br />\n<strong>Short description:</strong><br />\nSystem to provide work with main functions of document workflow:</p>\n<ul>\n	<li id="otstup">Registration of documents</li>\n	<li id="otstup">Document workflow on the all stages document processing</li>\n	<li id="otstup">Configuration of document workflow</li>\n	<li id="otstup">Control of execution</li>\n	<li id="otstup">Workflow for the citizen’s appeals</li>\n	<li id="otstup">Creation of document project</li>\n	<li id="otstup">Electronic archive of documents</li>\n	<li id="otstup">Configuration workflow for the document</li>\n	<li id="otstup">Configuration report</li>\n	<li id="otstup">Integration with others company’s solutions</li>\n	<li id="otstup">System administration</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Technologies and libraries:</strong> ASP.net MVC, Web API, WCF, SOAP, ADO.Net, LINQ, Web Services, JSON, AJAX, DevExpress, JS, HTML<br />\n<strong>Frameworks:</strong> ASP.Net, Entity Framework<br />\n<strong>DB:</strong> MS SQL/Oracle/PostgreSQL</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'MANAGEMENT SYSTEM DOCUMENT', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '492-autosave-v1', '', '', '2018-09-27 15:42:12', '2018-09-27 15:42:12', '', 492, 'http://demo.pinofran.com/demo/SoftWareSolutionsWP/index.php/2018/09/27/492-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
