(588, 1, '2018-09-27 15:38:53', '2018-09-27 15:38:53', '<p>Project works since 2016.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Customer: </strong>International Corporation</p>\r\n<p><strong>Goals: </strong></p>\r\n<p>Creating a logically unified information space for the management of supply and sale in real time. Getting plan and account information on the every level of company management. For achievement goals need to realize integration all solutions which using in company. Main software’s in company are Windchil, Vendavo, SAP, PRM, E-leader and LPOS. </p>\r\n<p><strong>Short description:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Main system modules:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li id="otstup">Product Management</li>\r\n	<li id="otstup">Supply and Demand</li>\r\n	<li id="otstup">Market Analysis</li>\r\n	<li id="otstup">Sales Target</li>\r\n	<li id="otstup">Order Status</li>\r\n	<li id="otstup">Main KPI</li>\r\n	<li id="otstup">Administration</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Technologies and libraries:</strong> ASP.net MVC, Web API, WCF, SOAP, ADO.Net, LINQ, Web Services, JSON, AJAX, DevExpress, JS, HTML</p>\r\n<p><strong>Frameworks:</strong> ASP.Net, Entity Framework</p>\r\n<p><strong>DB:</strong> MS SQL</p>', 'MANAGEMENT SYSTEM FOR SUPPLY AND SALE', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '496-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-09-27 15:38:53', '2018-09-27 15:38:53', '', 496, 'http://demo.pinofran.com/demo/SoftWareSolutionsWP/index.php/2018/09/27/496-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(589, 1, '2018-09-27 15:39:41', '2018-09-27 15:39:41', '<p>Project works since 2016.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Customer: </strong>bank</p>\r\n<p><strong>Goal:</strong><br />\r\nThe system allows custom authentication and authorization based upon an LDAP directory. In an organization, users and groups are stored in an LDAP directory. All the intranet applications are supposed to use this directory for authentication and authorization, to implement SSO. Development of common system for these applications to use for such authentication and authorization. A user if logged-in into one application, he should be able to use the other application w/o re-login.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Short description:</strong></p>\r\n<p>The system is composed of the following components: </p>\r\n<p>1. Web application</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Contains a log in page where users accessing intranet applications are redirected for authentication</li>\r\n	<li>Authenticates users against the LDAP directory, for the log in page</li>\r\n	<li>Keeps track of currently authenticated users, for later validations</li>\r\n	<li>Provides authorization data like user groups</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>2. HTTP module</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Provides custom authentication and authorization for the .NET applications</li>\r\n	<li>Authenticates every request to an application</li>\r\n	<li>Reporting</li>\r\n	<li>Administration</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Technologies and libraries:</strong> Webforms, Web API, WCF, WPF, SOAP, Web Services, JSON, AJAX, JS,HTML</p>\r\n<p><strong>Frameworks:</strong> ASP.Net, DevExpress XPO</p>\r\n<p><strong>DB:</strong> MS SQL</p>', 'CREATE THE ARCHITECTURE AND DESIGN OF AN LDAP BASED SINGLE SIGN ON SYSTEM (SSO). IMPLEMENT THE SYSTEM’S SERVICES AND APPLICATIONS', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '494-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-09-27 15:39:41', '2018-09-27 15:39:41', '', 494, 'http://demo.pinofran.com/demo/SoftWareSolutionsWP/index.php/2018/09/27/494-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(590, 1, '2018-09-27 15:42:51', '2018-09-27 15:42:51', '<p>Project works since 2015.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Customer: </strong>government institution</p>\r\n<p><strong>Goals:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Development of management system document for the hierarchical organization. Organization must be able to work without paper document. Company management have to get full control on the all stages work with document and task. System have to work with large number of users (more than 15000 users) and to save all documents of customs. System have to provide configuration workflow of document, reports without developers. System must to work using web-technologies and to provide 7-24 service. </p>\r\n<p><strong>Short description:</strong></p>\r\n<p>System to provide work with main functions of document workflow:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li id="otstup">Registration of documents</li>\r\n	<li id="otstup">Document workflow on the all stages document processing</li>\r\n	<li id="otstup">Configuration of document workflow</li>\r\n	<li id="otstup">Control of execution</li>\r\n	<li id="otstup">Workflow for the citizen’s appeals</li>\r\n	<li id="otstup">Creation of document project</li>\r\n	<li id="otstup">Electronic archive of documents</li>\r\n	<li id="otstup">Configuration workflow for the document</li>\r\n	<li id="otstup">Configuration report</li>\r\n	<li id="otstup">Integration with others company’s solutions</li>\r\n	<li id="otstup">System administration</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Technologies and libraries:</strong> ASP.net MVC, Web API, WCF, SOAP, ADO.Net, LINQ, Web Services, JSON, AJAX, DevExpress, JS, HTML</p>\r\n<p><strong>Frameworks:</strong> ASP.Net, Entity Framework</p>\r\n<p><strong>DB:</strong> MS SQL/Oracle/PostgreSQL</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'MANAGEMENT SYSTEM DOCUMENT', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '492-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-09-27 15:42:51', '2018-09-27 15:42:51', '', 492, 'http://demo.pinofran.com/demo/SoftWareSolutionsWP/index.php/2018/09/27/492-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(591, 1, '2018-09-27 15:53:13', '2018-09-27 15:53:13', '<p>Project works since 2014.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Customer: </strong>government institution</p>\r\n<p><strong>Goals: </strong></p>\r\n<p>Formations database of user actions on the base packages sent his computers to the network. System have to form database about all actions of user in network and to save this information long time. </p>\r\n<p><strong>Short description:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li id="otstup">Automatic processing of each packets sent user''s computer in the network</li>\r\n	<li id="otstup">Automatic building the session of each user on the network</li>\r\n	<li id="otstup">Automatic creation of report with date, time, data (IP address, port, MAC address) sender and recipient</li>\r\n	<li id="otstup">Analysis session data on the defined rules, information about his violation</li>\r\n	<li id="otstup">Definition hacker parameters who try to penetrate in to corporate network</li>\r\n	<li id="otstup">Automatic functioning without administrator and the ability to define holes in information security</li>\r\n	<li id="otstup">Processing data in others topology (local and cloud)</li>\r\n	<li id="otstup">Reporting</li>\r\n	<li id="otstup">System administration</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>System architecture built by using technology Big Data.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Programming language: </strong>Java EE </p>\r\n<p><strong>Frameworks:</strong> Hadoop, Apache Storm</p>\r\n<p><strong>DB:</strong> Hbase (NoSQL)</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'ANALYSIS OF NETWORK TRAFFIC', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '490-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-09-27 15:53:13', '2018-09-27 15:53:13', '', 490, 'http://demo.pinofran.com/demo/SoftWareSolutionsWP/index.php/2018/09/27/490-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
