(652, 1, '2018-09-29 09:28:59', '2018-09-29 09:28:59', '<p>Project works since 2009.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Goals:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Development, implementation and support high load management system insurance company. System have to work with large number of users (more than 15000 users) and provide all business processes of insurance company. System have to provide configuration insurance products, reports without developers. System must to work using web-technologies and to provide 7-24 service.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Short description:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Solution have all business processes for creation, support and management insurance contracts. </p>\r\n<p><strong>System include modules:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Insurance contract</li>\r\n	<li>Configuration of insurance products</li>\r\n	<li>Configuration of reports</li>\r\n	<li>CRM</li>\r\n	<li>E-insurance</li>\r\n	<li>Insurance service payment</li>\r\n	<li>Account with insurance broker and agent</li>\r\n	<li>Workplace agent/broker</li>\r\n	<li>Payment insurance services with bankcard</li>\r\n	<li>System administration</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Expansion of project:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Development of mobile application</li>\r\n	<li>Integration with others client''s software and site</li>\r\n	<li>Integration with contact center (API phone)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Technologies and libraries:</strong> ASP.NET Webforms, Web API, WCF, SOAP, ADO.Net, LINQ, Web Services, JSON, AJAX, DevExpress, JS, HTML</p>\r\n<p><strong>Mobile:</strong> Java for Android</p>\r\n<p><strong>Frameworks</strong> ASP.Net, Entity Framework</p>\r\n<p><strong>DB:</strong> MS SQL</p>\r\n<p>Now project is in support and development</p>', 'MANAGEMENT SYSTEM INSURANCE COMPANY', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '486-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-09-29 09:28:59', '2018-09-29 09:28:59', '', 486, 'http://demo.pinofran.com/demo/SoftWareSolutionsWP/index.php/2018/09/29/486-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(653, 1, '2018-09-29 09:38:36', '2018-09-29 09:38:36', '<p>Our team participate project in the HMI development for upcoming Mercedes-Benz model.</p>\r\n<p>Project mostly based on C++/Qt/QML, uses Linux environment. Between separated components networking is used. </p>\r\n<p><strong>Our responsibility on that project: </strong></p>\r\n<p>Features: </p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Architecture design of several components</li>\r\n	<li>UI implementation (QML):\r\n          \r\n<ul>\r\n              \r\n	<li>Implementation of base components, screens, menus, transitions, graphical effects</li>\r\n\r\n          </ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>C++ plugins implementation:</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Implementation of intermediate level between UI and backend </p>\r\n<p>Networking communication with backend, data processing and preparation for visualization at UI side</p>\r\n<p>Handling events coming from backend</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Implementation of mock backend, C#:</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Implementation of mock server - hardware functions &amp; activity emulation (ignition, seats settings, engine status/settings, lights, sensors, etc…)</p>', 'Automotive industry', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '474-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-09-29 09:38:36', '2018-09-29 09:38:36', '', 474, 'http://demo.pinofran.com/demo/SoftWareSolutionsWP/index.php/2018/09/29/474-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(654, 1, '2018-09-29 09:42:35', '2018-09-29 09:42:35', '<p>Our team participate project in the HMI development for upcoming Mercedes-Benz model.</p>\r\n<p>Project mostly based on C++/Qt/QML, uses Linux environment. Between separated components networking is used. </p>\r\n<p><strong>Our responsibility on that project: </strong></p>\r\n<p>Features: </p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Architecture design of several components</li>\r\n	<li>UI implementation (QML):       \r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Implementation of base components, screens, menus, transitions, graphical effects</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>C++ plugins implementation:\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Implementation of intermediate level between UI and backend</li>\r\n<li>Networking communication with backend, data processing and preparation for visualization at UI side</li>\r\n<li>Handling events coming from backend</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Implementation of mock backend, C#:\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Implementation of mock server - hardware functions &amp; activity emulation (ignition, seats settings, engine status/settings, lights, sensors, etc…)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Automotive industry', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '474-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-09-29 09:42:35', '2018-09-29 09:42:35', '', 474, 'http://demo.pinofran.com/demo/SoftWareSolutionsWP/index.php/2018/09/29/474-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(655, 1, '2018-09-29 09:44:45', '2018-09-29 09:44:45', '<p>Our team participate project in the HMI development for upcoming Mercedes-Benz model.</p>\r\n<p>Project mostly based on C++/Qt/QML, uses Linux environment. Between separated components networking is used. </p>\r\n<p><strong>Our responsibility on that project: </strong></p>\r\n<p>Features:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Architecture design of several components</li>\r\n	<li>UI implementation (QML):\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Implementation of base components, screens, menus, transitions, graphical effects</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>C++ plugins implementation:\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Implementation of intermediate level between UI and backend</li>\r\n	<li>Networking communication with backend, data processing and preparation for visualization at UI side</li>\r\n	<li>Handling events coming from backend</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Implementation of mock backend, C#:\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Implementation of mock server - hardware functions &amp; activity emulation (ignition, seats settings, engine status/settings, lights, sensors, etc…)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Automotive industry', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '474-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-09-29 09:44:45', '2018-09-29 09:44:45', '', 474, 'http://demo.pinofran.com/demo/SoftWareSolutionsWP/index.php/2018/09/29/474-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(656, 1, '2018-09-29 09:49:19', '2018-09-29 09:49:19', '<p><strong>Segment:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Security, Multimedia, Networking </p>\r\n<p><strong>Short description:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Secure audio processing &amp; management system. </p>\r\n<p><strong>Details:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Audio stream processing (RTSP, RTP, ICY, etc…)</li>\r\n	<li>Audio streams management (convert 3rd party streams to PCM; layer management)</li>\r\n	<li>Unit testing, test cases development</li>\r\n	<li>Inter-process communication (IPC) development</li>\r\n	<li>3rd party protocol processing (Pandora protocol)</li>\r\n	<li>Media utilities development (parsing playlists, metadata, additional info)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Technologies: </strong>C/C++11, Boost, CMake, SVN/Git, CUnit, CppUnit, Qt unit test, Google C++ Testing Framework, SQLite, OpenSSL, Networking, Embedded systems, Linux, Postresql, audio management</p>', 'Audio processing system', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '470-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-09-29 09:49:19', '2018-09-29 09:49:19', '', 470, 'http://demo.pinofran.com/demo/SoftWareSolutionsWP/index.php/2018/09/29/470-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(657, 1, '2018-09-29 09:50:28', '2018-09-29 09:50:28', '<p><strong>Segment:</strong></p>\n<p>Security, Analysis, Reverse engineering </p>\n<p><strong>Short description:</strong></p>\n<p>Linux daemon provides two functions:</p>\n<ul><li>Monitors applications activity, sends security reports to special server</li><li>Provides applications activity control, based on behavioral action patterns</li></ul><p>Our responsibility:</p><ul><li>Parallelizing existing code</li><li>Integration with other projects</li></ul><p><strong>Technologies: </strong>C++, CppUnit</p>', 'Anti-Malware Protection', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '476-autosave-v1', '', '', '2018-09-29 09:50:28', '2018-09-29 09:50:28', '', 476, 'http://demo.pinofran.com/demo/SoftWareSolutionsWP/index.php/2018/09/29/476-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(658, 1, '2018-09-29 09:50:30', '2018-09-29 09:50:30', '<p><strong>Segment:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Security, Analysis, Reverse engineering </p>\r\n<p><strong>Short description:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Linux daemon provides two functions:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Monitors applications activity, sends security reports to special server</li>\r\n	<li>Provides applications activity control, based on behavioral action patterns</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Our responsibility:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Parallelizing existing code</li>\r\n	<li>Integration with other projects</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Technologies: </strong>C++, CppUnit</p>', 'Anti-Malware Protection', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '476-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-09-29 09:50:30', '2018-09-29 09:50:30', '', 476, 'http://demo.pinofran.com/demo/SoftWareSolutionsWP/index.php/2018/09/29/476-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
